{"tid":753074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘彩德邨山邊採野菇進食　49歲婦中毒入院","createTime":"2018-07-23T10:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T03:21:13.000Z","uid":75969,"like":473,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"e623c882e1c0df0c8af9c6ef769275df4c0f8dca","tid":753074,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/photo/bkn-20180723172819865-0723_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180723175822\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180723172819865-0723_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180723175822&h=d3abab91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">女病人進食野菇後出現中毒病徵，到基督教聯合醫院急症室求診。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心正調查一宗懷疑進食野生菇類後引致食物中毒的個案，一名49歲女病人昨(22日)在家中進食菇類約2小時後，出現腹痛、嘔吐和腹瀉等病徵。她同日到基督教聯合醫院急症室求診，現時情況穩定。初步調查顯示，病人於7月21日在觀塘彩德邨附近的山邊採摘所進食的野生菇類，並加入豬肉炒成菜餚。<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，該名女病人為非香港居民的華人</span>，而其進食的菇類品種未明。<br />\n<br />\n防護中心發言人表示，進食菇類而引致的食物中毒一般為急性，病徵大多包括進食後短時間內出現惡心、嘔吐和腹痛等腸道徵狀。因應不同的菇種，病人亦可能出現如大量流汗、幻覺、昏迷或其他神經系統病徵和肝衰竭，嚴重者更可能引致死亡。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調，由於難於辨別菇類是否適宜食用，提醒市民切勿採摘野生菇類進食。如市民懷疑因進食菇類引致食物中毒，應立即求醫。如有剩餘菇菌，應帶同前往求醫，以供辨識種類。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署數字顯示，因進食野生採摘菇類引致食物中毒個案在2016年有2宗，2人受影響；2017年則有3宗，有4人受影響；今年截至7月22日有2宗，4人受影響，但不包括今次的個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/bkn-20180723172819865-0723_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fbkn-20180723172819865-0723_00822_001.html&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6dc27adf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/bkn-20180723172819865-0723_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71047b45227f9015ad0c7a3a5394660193ff1169","tid":753074,"uid":195920,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"02809bf9d63170bc6a0d20aa028cfc81ed8b3818","tid":753074,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e419dac67a71f621cad79a65c67edf9321eaede","tid":753074,"uid":138006,"like":4,"dislike":224,"score":-220,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"比d同情心啦 人地初來乍到唔知而亂摘姐"},{"pid":"aa41874fb8ba0b9e034560a18f9d99cf5e949213","tid":753074,"uid":176366,"like":136,"dislike":2,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"達爾文：屌"},{"pid":"31dc60389b28130313455b99e984cd7eab5682ee","tid":753074,"uid":3646,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"非香港人的華人<br />\n<br />\n咁就抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9227f39c8f928d6c28bfa39ff65234da361b82","tid":753074,"uid":127299,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"找清條數先好出院"},{"pid":"f70831ae4c25628c880a483d0c0050b6b7331067","tid":753074,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31dc60389b28130313455b99e984cd7eab5682ee","tid":753074,"uid":3646,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"非香港人的華人<br />\n<br />\n咁就抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"雙程證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e5b92b8380808a8e1daf916ffa2b35fb4b35d0","tid":753074,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"e84391a80988664a28ad6ab5843d2f62c0d6a23c","tid":753074,"uid":8048,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:24:34.